Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,這本是一個平凡的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,渴求著寧靜的日夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:13.76,Default1,,0,0,0,,期盼著與遠方親友的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,但來訪的卻是突然的襲擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.49,Default1,,0,0,0,,邂逅… 激鬥… 巨大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:27.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,命運的詩篇靜靜拉開帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.61,Default1,,0,0,0,,暴風驟雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:33.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,將希望託付於永恆的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:37.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,魔法少女奈葉A's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:39.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.38,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎？ 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,哎{\fnSimhe}～{\r}？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:50.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過 我很期待見到菲特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:52.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,連我們都如此期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:00.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,與菲特擁有共同回憶的奈葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,自然會更加期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.89,Default1,,0,0,0,,聽說菲特會這裡玩 奈葉真是好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:10.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:17.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,得儘早策劃菲特的歡迎會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:19.72,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,好好慶祝一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,在誰家裡舉行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.35,Default1,,0,0,0,,在「翠屋」如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:43.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,#2 \N\N激鬥的風雨再次降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.46,Default1,,0,0,0,,對平民施加魔法攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,這可是重罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.97,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,是管理局的魔導師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,時空管理局非常任魔導師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,只要伏法 妳便有辯護的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.35,Default1,,0,0,0,,如果同意 就繳械投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,誰會投降啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾 奈葉就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.41,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:47.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特的審判結束後 我們便試圖聯繫奈葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,結果通訊無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,透過管理局的調查\N\N發現這裡展開了廣域結界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.56,Default1,,0,0,0,,所以 我們慌忙趕了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.82,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,那個人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:05.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,為何襲擊奈葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,事情太過突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,有菲特在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:25.55,Default1,,0,0,0,,雷光戰斧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.26,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Arc Saber{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}弧光飛刃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,鋼鐵伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.69,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H81111EE&)}Schwalbefliegen{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}雲燕翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:41.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,屏障！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.65,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H81111EE&)\fad(0,200)}Panzerhindernis{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}精鋼屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8299BE8&)}屏障──
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:08.88,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H8299BE8&}──破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:16.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.15,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H81111EE&)}Pferde{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}駿風騎乘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.57,Default1,,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,想打爛她很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,但那樣做沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,必須取得她的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.93,Default1,,0,0,0,,還剩下２發魔力彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,能成功嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙也來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:11.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛諾他們也暫停阿斯拉的整備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.45,Default1,,0,0,0,,正趕往這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,阿萊克斯 還沒找到結界密碼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,還需一些時間才能解析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,術式與我們不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.43,Default1,,0,0,0,,這不是「米德芝爾達」式的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.22,Default1,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是哪裡的魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳這傢伙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.00,Default1,,0,0,0,,交待出名字 出身世界 和妳的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,提高警覺！ 菲特！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,希格娜姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.19,Default1,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔劍 魔力彈裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.73,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Explosion{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}魔力爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8963696&)}紫電一閃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.62,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H00BBBB&)}Defenser{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}護禦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:02.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.19,Default1,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:05.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,我必須去幫她們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,靈妙的韻律 化作光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:15.66,Default1,,0,0,0,,將鋼鐵護壁賦予治癒之環
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是回復與防禦的結界魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉絕不要走出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,大意了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,我正打算逆轉形勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:44.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,看來是我多此一舉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過 可不要亂來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,萬一妳受了傷 主人會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.79,Default1,,0,0,0,,我知道啦 真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:07.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是妳掉下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.67,Default1,,0,0,0,,已經幫妳修復了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.13,Default1,,0,0,0,,謝謝… 希格娜姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,戰況實質上是三對三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,既然是一對一 我們貝爾卡的騎士…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.10,Default1,,0,0,0,,絕不會輸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,咦？ 「闇之書」不見了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:42.62,Default1,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:43.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 尤諾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.02,Default1,,0,0,0,,雷光戰斧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.25,Default1,,0,0,0,,中樞沒有受損
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.13,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Recovery{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}自我修復
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:07.93,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾 必須將全員同時從結界內傳送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,做得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.61,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯 只要能與艾爾芙協力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,應該能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,我來牽制敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,能利用這時間來準備嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:20.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙也聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.53,Default1,,0,0,0,,情況非常不利…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:26.65,Default1,,0,0,0,,我會盡力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.17,Default1,,0,0,0,,大家都加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:32.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.15,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.14,Default1,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊 妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,是疾風嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.90,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是莎瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.09,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:45.39,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起 我還沒買到橄欖油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,我去遠處超市再找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:54.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊 不必費那麼大的勁去找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,我可以順路把大家都接回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.68,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起 今晚不能幫妳做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.20,Default1,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.18,Default1,,0,0,0,,我會儘快回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊 不必著急的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.35,Default1,,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:18.36,Default1,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.48,Default1,,0,0,0,,待會兒見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.95,Default1,,0,0,0,,要儘快把事情辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,風精之戒 為我指引道路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.54,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Ja.{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.04,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Pendelform{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}鐘擺形態
