Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔劍 展開我的護甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.44,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\t(\bord4\3c&H8963696&)}Panzergeist{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}英魄靈鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.91,Default1,,0,0,0,,馳騁吧 發射！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,作為魔導師 妳確實不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.47,Default1,,0,0,0,,但是 想與貝爾卡騎士一對一交鋒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.60,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳還差得遠！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔劍 一刀兩斷吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.36,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jawohl
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.33,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「遵命」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.83,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.93,Default1,,0,0,0,,傳送的準備已經做好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.85,Default1,,0,0,0,,卻無法打破空間結界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,我也盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.36,Default1,,0,0,0,,但這道結界好堅固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.83,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Nachladen{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}彈倉裝填
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.70,Default1,,0,0,0,,就是它…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.29,Default1,,0,0,0,,那魔力彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:44.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,那是短時間提高魔力的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:45.84,Default1,,0,0,0,,到此為止了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,那就老實一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.08,Default1,,0,0,0,,只要不反抗 我也不會殺妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,誰會聽妳擺佈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,氣魄不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:01.77,Default1,,0,0,0,,我是貝爾卡的騎士──\N\N「守護騎士」的將領 希格娜姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.40,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是我的愛劍── 「烈焰魔劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.44,Default1,,0,0,0,,妳叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,米德芝爾達的魔導師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,時空管理局非常任局員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}泰斯塔羅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.74,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是「雷光戰斧」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.50,Default1,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔羅莎… 還有雷光戰斧嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.16,Default1,,0,0,0,,必須去幫助大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,我必須去幫助大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.75,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Master{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.88,Faqi,,0,0,0,,Shooting Mode Acceleration{\fs22}\N\N{\fs66}射擊模式 全面開放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.02,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「我們發射『星光聚裂』吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.02,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's shoot it, Starlight Breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,不行啊… 你的狀態無法承受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.57,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「我可以發射」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.57,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can be shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,如果使用那種大負荷魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.54,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心會毀壞的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.62,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「我相信妳 主人」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.62,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I believe master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.38,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\fs66}「也相信我吧 主人」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.38,Faqi,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Trust me, my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,既然旭日之心相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,那麼我也相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:07.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.52,Default1,,0,0,0,,尤諾君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:09.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,艾爾芙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.24,Default1,,0,0,0,,我來負責破壞結界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.58,Default1,,0,0,0,,你們看準時機傳送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:16.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.78,Default1,,0,0,0,,奈葉… 妳能行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:23.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.96,Default1,,0,0,0,,我用「星光聚裂」來粉碎結界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.42,Default1,,0,0,0,,旭日之心 倒數計時吧
