Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,這… 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.32,Default1,,0,0,0,,怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,這群傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.21,Default1,,0,0,0,,結界被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:38.23,Default1,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.11,Default1,,0,0,0,,莎瑪爾 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:41.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,多虧妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:42.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.07,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們先分頭撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.12,Default1,,0,0,0,,然後在老地方集合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.51,Default1,,0,0,0,,她們要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:08.73,Default1,,0,0,0,,快點鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.75,Default1,,0,0,0,,追逐傳送蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:12.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,我們正在盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:16.37,Default1,,0,0,0,,那是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:22.99,Default1,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.27,Default1,,0,0,0,,趕快把醫療班傳送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:28.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,開啟中繼傳送門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:32.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,還有 聯繫總局的醫療設施
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:33.05,Default1,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:36.64,Default1,,0,0,0,,不行了 鎖定失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.30,Default1,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:42.94,Default1,,0,0,0,,對不起 克洛諾君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.03,Default1,,0,0,0,,我失敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:48.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛諾君…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:55.28,Default1,,0,0,0,,一級搜索指定太古遺產…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:22:56.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,「闇之書」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:03.06,Default1,,0,0,0,,克洛諾君 你知道它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:04.71,Default1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:07.63,Default1,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:12.59,Default1,,0,0,0,,與它有一段不願回憶的因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:10.87,Default1,,0,0,0,,這次事件充滿了謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:13.80,Default1,,0,0,0,,事情的真相似乎很複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.13,0:25:17.33,Default1,,0,0,0,,不過 奈葉和菲特終於再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.39,0:25:21.34,Default1,,0,0,0,,而且 還有另外一件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.09,0:25:26.26,Default1,,0,0,0,,下集 魔法少女奈葉A's 第3話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.54,0:25:28.98,Default1,,0,0,0,,再會與搬家！
